node.text: @msrachelhollis👇 (link in bio) We talk about loving yourself and seeing failure as success. We all need to learn to see the positive aspects of every failure in our life, to take proper care of ourselves by taking good care of our health, to sit down and process pain and grief at our own pace, and to never lose ourselves just to keep a relationship.

node.text: It can be devastating when a friend or partner betrays your trust. Even more so when in searching for reasons for the betrayal, we end up blaming ourselves. But remember that you are not to blame for other people's poor judgement or behavior.

node.text:
Honored & grateful for this profile in @wsjmag about my journey so far. It’s so important to look back and reflect for each of us and it is as important to look forward and consistently redefine ourselves for the future. There have been many rejections, many failures and mistakes along the way but at the same time there has been love, joy and so many fulfilling opportunities. The thing I’m most grateful for is the fact that I get to connect with so many of you, from different backgrounds and walks of life. I love seeing school teachers show my videos in their classrooms, or frontline workers reading my book, or the millions of you that listen to the podcast every week through to people in the worlds of business, music and entertainment. All of you matter and all of you have a purpose. If I can help you find, ignite and live your purpose so that you can serve the world then my life will be a success. ⁠⁠
⁠⁠
I want to express my deepest, sincerest appreciation to anyone that has helped and supported me, consciously or unconsciously along the way. This is just the beginning!

Stylist @hemaapersad 
Hair @themensgroomer 
Outfit @yony_la

The *way* you receive determines *what* you receive. Comment a 💛 below if you needed this @jayshettygenius post today. ⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Maintaining a state of gratitude and love only leads to greater abundance in your life 💫⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Deliberate love creates deeper love.⁠⁠
Consistent light creates brighter light.⁠⁠
Intentional hope creates stronger hope.⁠⁠
⁠⁠
This is what @jayshettygenius is all about. Weekly workshops, guided meditations, and a community centered in holistic well-being 🙏 ⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Become a member today and I'll see you in the next workshop. Link in bio to join now! 👉 jayshettygenius.com
